This is a simple Docker file and Mojolicious app

It is inteded to be used as a starting point for Dockerising Perl Mojolicious applications

The default port of 8080

to build after cloning this repo:

$ cd DockerMojo
$ docker build -t mojo_app .

$ docker images
REPOSITORY          TAG                 IMAGE ID            CREATED             VIRTUAL SIZE
mojo_app            latest              982b597d1551        7 hours ago         360.9 MB
ubuntu              14.04               03419f0ebb31        2 weeks ago         196.6 MB

to initialy run:

$ docker run -p 8080 -t -i --name mojo_app mojo_app
or
$ docker run -p 8080 -d -t -i --name mojo_app mojo_app

$ docker inspect mojo_app
...
 "IPAddress": "172.17.0.2",
...
Write to the browser:
172.17.0.2:8080

see it running:

$ docker ps
CONTAINER ID        IMAGE                      COMMAND                CREATED             STATUS              PORTS                    NAMES
bb91f7d6838a        mojo_app:latest   				 "/bin/sh -c 'hypnoto   2 minutes ago       Up 2 minutes        0.0.0.0:8080->8080/tcp   mojo_app     

check on running processes:

$ top mojo_app
UID                 PID                 PPID                C                   STIME               TTY                 TIME                CMD
root                14733               1886                0                   14:58               pts/20              00:00:00            /bin/sh -c hypnotoad -f script/my_app
root                14773               14733               0                   14:58               pts/20              00:00:00            /srv/www/my_app/script/my_app
root                14774               14773               0                   14:58               pts/20              00:00:00            /srv/www/my_app/script/my_app
root                14775               14773               0                   14:58               pts/20              00:00:00            /srv/www/my_app/script/my_app
root                14776               14773               0                   14:58               pts/20              00:00:00            /srv/www/my_app/script/my_app
root                14777               14773               0                   14:58               pts/20              00:00:00            /srv/www/my_app/script/my_app

stop the app running:

$ docker stop  mojo_app

start the app running again:

$ docker start mojo_app
